{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab {\b Project Management:} Planning and coordination of research activities including distribution of tasks, manufacturing devices, conducting experiments, collecting, analyzing and reporting data.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa0 \li720 \fi-360 \endash \tx360\tab {\b Data Collection:} Utilizing NIdaq devices (National Instruments Inc.) to acquire electrophysiological signals in real time. Collecting video images (Allied Vision Inc.) for offline movement analysis.\par}
